quran[98]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaaf-- Haa—Yaa – Ain-- Soaad."
  19,2,"(Woi yε) nkaebͻ fa ahummͻborͻ a wo Wura Nyankopͻn de huu N’akoa Zakariya mmͻbͻ;"
  19,3,"Ɛberε a osu frεε ne Wura Nyankopͻn wͻ kokoa mu no."
  19,4,"Ɔkaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, me honam mu nnompe nyinaa ago, na me tri nwii nso ahura dwono fitaa, na su a mesu frε Woͻ no mu biara nnihͻ a, ansi me yie."
  19,5,"Na mesuro me nkorͻfoͻ a εwͻ m’akyi; me yere nso ayε bonini, enti dom me kyԑ me (ba anaasε) okyitaafoͻ a ofri Wo hͻ-"
  19,6,"a, ɔbɛdi m’adeε na wadi Yakobo asefoͻ adeε. Me Wura Nyankopͻn, yε (saa abͻfra a Wode no bεma me) no obia Wogye no to mu “."
  19,7,"(Soro abɔfoɔ kaa sɛ) “Zakariya, Yεde abarimaa bi rehyε wo bͻ, yεfrε no Yah’ya (Yohane) Yenii kan ntoo obi din te saa “."
  19,8,"Zakariya kaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, εbεyε dεn na manya ba aberε a meyere yε bonini, nokorε mu me nso manyin abᴐ akͻkora?”"
  19,9,"(Ɔbɔfoɔ no) kaa sε: “Saa (ara na εbεyε). Wo Wura Nyankopͻn se: “Ɛyε mmrε ma Me, nokorε sε Medii kan bͻͻ wo a, (saa berε no) na wonyε hwee“"
  19,10,"Zakariya kaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, ma me (ho) nsεnkyerεnee. (Onyankopͻn) kaa sε: Wo nsεnkyerεnee ne sε, (εwom sε) wote apͻ deε, nanso wo (nntumi) nkasa nnipa ho nnansa."
  19,11,"Enti opue fri pie no mu baa ne nkorͻfoͻ no hͻ, na ͻde nsεnkyerεnee kasa kyerεε wͻn sε: “Momͻ (Nyankopͻn) abodin anͻpa ne anwummerε “."
  19,12,"Yahaya, fa ahoᴐden sᴐ Nwoma no mu; na Yԑmaa no adwen wᴐ ne nkᴐdaa berԑ mu,"
  19,13,"San (maa no) nti mmͻborͻ akoma a efri Yεn hͻ, san yԑԑ no (nipa) kronkron; na ͻyε obi a osuro Nyame."
  19,14,"Na ͻyε ayεmyε ma n’awofoͻ, na ͻnyε ahomasoͻ (nipa, anaa) asobrakyeε."
  19,15,"Asomdwoeε wͻ ne so wͻ εda a yεwoo no, εne da a owuiε ne εda a yεbenyane no aba nkwa mu."
  19,16,"Na kae Mar’yam nso (ho asԑm) wͻ Nwoma no mu. Ɛberε a ͻtwee ne ho frii n’abusuafoͻ ho kͻͻ apueɛ fam hͻ baabi."
  19,17,"Ɔfaa ntware mu twaree ͻne wͻn ntεm, ɛna Yεsomaa Yε honhom baa ne hͻ bεdaa ne ho adi kyerεε no tesε onipa sεso pεpεεpε."
  19,18,"Mar’yam kaa sε: “Mehwehwε Ahummͻborͻ Hene no hͻ ntwitwagyeε wͻ wo ho, sε woyε Nyamesuroni a."
  19,19,"(Ɔbͻfoͻ no) kaa sε: “Medeε meyε wo Wura Nyankopͻn bͻfoͻ; (Wasoma me) sε menfa abarimaa kronkron bi mεkyε wo “."
  19,20,"Mar’yam kaa sε: ”Ɛbεyε dεn na manya abarimaa aberε a ͻbarima mfaa ne ho nkaa me, na menyε odwammanfoͻ nso?"
  19,21,"(Ɔbͻfoͻ no) kaa sε: “Saa ara na (εbεyε); wo Wura Nyankopͻn aka sε: “Ɛyε mmrε ma Me. Sεdeε Yεbεyε no nsεnkyerεnee ne ahummͻborͻ a efri Yεn hͻ ama nnipa. Ԑyε asεm a yɛahyehyε awie”."
  19,22,"Enti (Mar’yam) nyinsεn (abͻfra) no; na ͻtwee ne ho de (nyinsεn) no kͻͻ akyirikyiri baabi."
  19,23,"Awoͻ yeaa no de no kͻͻ akyiresua dua bi ho. Ɔkaa sε: “Ɛkaa menko a anka medii kan wui ansa na (asεm) woi (reba), anka yεwerε afri me koraa”."
  19,24,"Enti (εnee bi) fri n’ase frεε no sε: “Ɛmma wo werε nho, wo Wura Nyankopͻn ayε asuwa bi wͻ w'ase hͻ."
  19,25,"Woso akyiresua dua no bra w'anim na akyiresua aba foforͻ a abereε bεte atͻ wo so."
  19,26,"Di, na nom na ma w’ani nnye. Sε wohu onipa biara a, ka sε: “Mahyε Ahummͻborͻ Hene no akͻmkyene ho bͻ, enti menkasa onipa biara ho nnε“."
  19,27,"Mar’yam faa (abͻfra) no de no baa n’abusuafoͻ hͻ. “Wͻkaa sε: “Nokorε sε wode awanwadeε aba (fie)“."
  19,28,"Aaron nua baa, na wopapa nyε onipa bͻneni, εna wo maame nso nyε (ͻbaa) dwamanfoͻ."
  19,29,"Enti Mar’yam (de nensa) kyerεε (abͻfra) no so. Wͻkaa sε: “Ɛbεyε dεn na yɛatumi ne akokoaa a ͻda tanaa mu akasa? “"
  19,30,"(Yesu) kaa sε:” Nokorε meyε Onyankopͻn akoa. Ɔde Nwoma no ama me, εna Wayε me ɔkͻmhyεni;"
  19,31,"Ɛna Wahyira me wͻ baabiara a me wͻ biara, εna Wayε Nyamefrε ne Zaka no nso nhyε ama me wͻ mmerε tenten a mete aseε,"
  19,32,"Ɛna (Onyankopͻn ahyε me sε menyε) ayεmyε ma me maame, na Wammͻ me (obi a meyε) ahomasoͻ anaa tibͻneni."
  19,33,"Asomdwoeε wͻ me so wͻ εda a yεwoo me, ne εda a mewuo ne εda a yεbenyane me aba nkwa mu bio."
  19,34,"Saa na Mar’yam ba Yesu no ho asεm no teε. (Woi ne Yesu ho) nokwasεm no a wͻregye ho akyinnyeε no."
  19,35,"Ɛmfata mma Nyankopͻn sε Ͻwo ba. Kronkron Hene ne no. Sε Ɔhyehyε biribi a, deε ͻka kyerε adekorͻ no ara ne sε: “Yε! na ayε “"
  19,36,"(Yesu kaa sε) : “Nokorε, Onyankopͻn ne me Wura, εna Ɔyε monso mo Wura, enti monsom no. Woi ne kwan tenenee no."
  19,37,"Nanso ntotoo bεtͻͻ akuo no ntεm (wͻ Yesu ho); enti due nka (Kaafirfoͻ) boniayεfoͻ no, wͻ Da kεseε no nhyiamu no ho."
  19,38,"Sεdeε wͻbɛsi ahunu adeε kann ate asεm kann wͻ Ɛda a wͻbεba Yεn hͻ no, nanso abͻneεfoͻ no wͻ ͻyera pefee mu nnε."
  19,39,"Enti (Ɔkͻmhyεni), bͻ wͻn kͻkͻ wͻ berεguo Da no ho, εberε a yεbɛdi asεm no awie no, nanso (seesei) wɔabu wͻn ani agu so a wͻn nnye nnie."
  19,40,"Nokorε sε, Yεn na Yɛbɛdi adeε wͻ asaase no soͻ na Yεn hͻ na wͻn (nyinaa) bεsan aba."
  19,41,"Na kae Abraham (ho asԑm) wͻ Nwoma no mu. Nokorε sε na ͻyε ɔkͻmhyεni nokwafoɔ."
  19,42,"Ɛberε a ͻka kyerεε n’agya sε: “M’agya, adεn na wosom adeε a εnte (asεm) na enhunu (adeε) na entumi mma wo mfasoͻ biara?"
  19,43,"M’agya, nokorε sε nimdeε aba me hͻ a ebi maa wo hͻ enti di m’akyi, na menkyerε wo kwan tenenee no."
  19,44,"M’agya, hwε na woansom bonsam. Nokorε sε ͻbonsam ate Ahummͻborͻ Hene no so atua."
  19,45,"M’agya, nokorε, mesuro sε anhwε a na asotwee bi fri Ahummͻborͻ Hene no hͻ abεsͻ wo mu, na wo akͻyε ͻbonsam yͻnko.”"
  19,46,"(Ne papa) kaa sε: ”Abraham, wompε m’abosom no? Sε woanyae (wonsεm keka ne wo nneyεε no) a, mɛsi wo aboͻ. Enti fri me so kͻ akyirikyiri seesei ara”."
  19,47,"Abraham kaa sε: ”Asomdwoeε nka wo; mεsrε me Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ bͻnefakyε ama wo. Nokorε sε Ne yεm yε ma me”."
  19,48,"Matwe me ho afri mo ho, ne deε mofri Nyankopͻn akyi sufrε wͻn no, na meresu afrε me Wura Nyankopᴐn; na ebia mesufrε me Wura Nyankopᴐn a mesufrε no nnyε kwa."
  19,49,"Ɛberε a Abraham twee ne ho frii wͻn ho, ne deε wɔfri Nyankopɔn akyi som no ho no, Yεmaa no Is’haaq ne Ya’aquub, na Yεyεε wͻn (mu) biara nkכmhyεni."
  19,50,"Na Yεde Y'ahummͻborͻ dom wͻn, na Yεmaa amansan bͻͻ wͻn din pa."
  19,51,"Kae Mose nso wͻ Nwoma no mu. Nokorε sε na ͻyε (onipa) a yatu no asihͻ, na ͻyε Ɔsomafoͻ (san nso yε) nkɔmhyεni."
  19,52,"Yεfrεε no wͻ bepͻ (Sinai) nifa so hͻ, na Yεmaa no bεnee Yεn ne no dii nkutahoo."
  19,53,"Yefri Y’ahummͻborͻ mu dom no maa ne nua Aaron bεyεε nkͻmhyεni."
  19,54,"Kae Ishmael nso wͻ Nwoma no mu. Nokorε sε na odi nokorε wͻ bͻhyε no ho. Na ͻyε ͻsomafoͻ (san nso yε) nkͻmhyεni."
  19,55,"Na ͻhyε n’abusuafoͻ ma wͻ’frε Nyame san yi Zaka. Na (ͻyε nipa a) yagye no atom paa wͻ ne Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ."
  19,56,"Kae Idriis nso wͻ Nwoma no mu. Nokorε sε na ͻyε nkͻmhyεni nokwafoͻ."
  19,57,"Yεpegyaa no gyinaa gyinabrε a εkorͻn."
  19,58,"Saa nkorͻfoͻ yi na Nyankopͻn adom wͻn wͻ nkͻmhyεfoͻ no mu wͻ Adam asefoͻ no mu, ne wͻn a Yε’soaa wᴐn kaa Noa ho no mu, ne Abraham asefoͻ no, ne Israel (anaasε Yakobo asefoͻ no), ne wͻn a Yε’kyerɛε wͻn kwan, yii wͻn (wͻ adasamma mu no). Sε yεrekenkan Ahummͻborͻ Hene no Nsεm no kyerε wͻn a, wͻ’de wͻn ho kͻ fͻm de wͻn anim butu fͻm su."
  19,59,"Wͻn akyiri no, anaamusifoͻ bi besii wͻn anan mu a wͻ’buu wͻn ani guu Nyamefrε no soͻ, na wͻ’dii akͻnnͻ deε akyi. (Saa nkorͻfoͻ no) behyia ͻsεeε."
  19,60,"Gyesε wͻn a wͻbεsakra wͻn adwen na wagye adie, na wͻ’adi dwuma pa, saa nkorͻfoͻ no na wͻ’bewura Soro aheman no mu no, na yensisi wͻn wͻ hwee ho."
  19,61,"Aheman a εwͻ hͻ daa a, Ahummͻborͻ Hene no ahyε Nenkoa no ho bͻ a εwͻ kokoa mu no (emu na wͻ’bεtena). Nokorε sε Onyankopͻn bͻhyε bεyε hͻ."
  19,62,"Wͻ nnte nsεmhunu wͻhͻ, gyesε Asomdwiε. Wͻbenya wͻn akͻnhoma anͻpa ne anyumerε."
  19,63,"Saa na Aheman a Yεde bεma Yεn nkoa no a wͻsuroo Nyame no bedi adeε wͻ mu no siteε."
  19,64,"Yεn (Soro abͻfoͻ no) yensiane (mma asaase so) gyesε (εnam) wo Wura Nyankopͻn ahyεdeε so. Ɔno na deε εwͻ y’anim ne deε εwͻ y’akyi ne deε εwͻ ne mmienu mfinimfii (nyinaa) wͻ no. Wo Wura Nyankopͻn werε mmfi (hwee)."
  19,65,"Ɔsoro ne asaase ne deε εwͻ mfinmfii Wura (ne no), enti som no, na si abotrε wͻ Nesom no ho. Enti wonim obi a ͻne Nyankopͻn din sε?"
  19,66,"Onipa ka sε: “Ɛberε a m’awuo, mεsan anyane aba nkwa mu bio?”"
  19,67,"Enti onipa nkae sε, nokorε sε Yɛdii kan bͻͻ no aberε a na ͻnyε hwee?"
  19,68,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), mede wo Wura Nyankopͻn di nse sε: “Yε bεboa wͻn ne abonsamfoͻ no (nyinaa) ano, na Yεde wͻn abetwa Ogya no ho ahyia wͻ (wͻn) nkotodwe so."
  19,69,"Ansa na ekuo biara mu no, Yayiyi wͻn a na wͻyε den te Ahummͻborͻ Hene no so atua no."
  19,70,"Nokorε sε Yenim momu wͻn a wͻfata sε yεhye wͻn wͻ (Amanehu gya no) mu."
  19,71,"Momu biara betwam wͻ hͻ. Woi yε nhyehyεε a εwͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ a εbԑyε hͻ."
  19,72,"Afei Yebeyi wͻn a wͻsuroo Nyame no afri mu, na Yagya abͻneεfoͻ no wͻ mu (wͻ wͻn) nkotodwe so."
  19,73,"Sε yεrekenkan Yεn nsεm pefee no kyerε wͻn a, wͻn a wͻ nnye nnie no ka kyerε wͻn a wagye adie no sε: “Akuo mmienu yi (agyidiefoͻ ne kaafirfoͻ no) emu deε εwͻ hen na ekuta gyinabrε pa na (εwͻ) hyia-dan a edi mmu a abadwafoͻ papa paa wͻ?”"
  19,74,"Aman dodoͻ sεn na Yɛdii wͻn anim kan sεee wͻn a na wͻn wͻ nneεma pa ne nnipadua a εyε fε?"
  19,75,"(Nkͻmhyεni), kasε: “Obi a ͻwͻ ͻyera mu no, Ahummͻborͻ Hene no ma no berε tenten ma no kosi sε wͻ’behu deε yabͻ wͻn ho kͻkͻ no, sε εyε asotwee no, anaasε Dͻnhwere no. (Ԑhͻ na) wͻ’behu deε ne gyinabrε nyε, na n’asraafoͻ (anaa nedͻm) nni ahoͻden."
  19,76,"Nyankopͻn de tenenee bεka wͻn a wͻ’anya kwankyerε no ho. Na dwumadi pa a (εho akatua pa) wͻ hͻ daa no, εno na εyε wͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ, na (εno nso na εwͻ) akatua (pa) ne awieε pa."
  19,77,"Wahunu obi a ͻnnye Yεn Nsεm no nnie, na ͻkasε: “Yε’bεma me sika ne mma (wͻ mewuo akyi no)?”"
  19,78,"(Saa nnipa no) anya ahuntasԑm no ho nimdeε bi, anaasε wanya Ahummͻborͻ Hene no hͻ bͻhyε bi?"
  19,79,"Daabi, Yεbεtwerε deε ͻka no (nyinaa), na Yatwe asotwee no mu tenteenten ama no."
  19,80,"Na (newuo akyiri no) Yεbedi n’adeε a ͻreka ho asεm no, na ͻno nko ara aba Yεn hͻ."
  19,81,"Wͻn afri Nyankopͻn akyi afa anyame foforͻ sεdeε wͻbεma wͻn tumi."
  19,82,"Daabi, (saa Da no wͻn anyame no) bεpo ͻsom a na wͻsom wͻn no, na wͻbεyε atamfo atia wͻn."
  19,83,"Wonhunu sε Yεsoma abonsamfoͻ no ba boniayεfoͻ no so bεtoto gu wͻn asom bͻ wͻn ansͻn (ma wͻdi bͻne)?"
  19,84,"Enti εmpre woho wͻ wͻn ho; efrisε Yabu (nna no) bu paa ama wͻn."
  19,85,"Ɛda a Yεbεboa Nyamesurofoͻ no ano akͻ Ahummͻborͻ Hene no hͻ, tesε nnipa kuo bi a wͻrekͻgye animuonyam (anaa abasobͻdeε no),"
  19,86,"Yεbεka abͻneεfoͻ no nso akͻ Amane-hunu gyem tesε nyεmmoa bi a sukͻm de wͻn na yεreka wͻn akͻ nsuo mu no,"
  19,87,"(Saa Da no) obiara nni ntwitwagyeε ho tumi, gyesε obi a ͻne Ahummͻborͻ Hene no ayε apam (anaasε ͻne no ahyε bͻ)."
  19,88,"Wͻkeka sε: ”Ahummͻborͻ Hene no wᴐ ba “."
  19,89,"Nokorε sε mode abususεm aba."
  19,90,"Ɔsoro reyε asunsuan wᴐ ho na asaase nso reyε apaepae ama mmepͻ nso abubu gͻsͻgͻsͻ,"
  19,91,"Sε yabͻ ͻba din (anaasε wͻde awoͻ) asusu Ahummͻborͻ Hene no."
  19,92,"Ԑmfata mma Ahummͻborͻ Hene no sε ͻwᴐ ba."
  19,93,"Deε εwͻ soro ne asaase so no mu biara ba Ahummͻborͻ Hene no hͻ wͻ akoa din mu."
  19,94,"Nokorε sε, Nyankopͻn Nim wͻn dodoͻ, na W’akan wͻn kan paa."
  19,95,"Wusᴐreԑ da no wͻn mu biara nko ara na εbεba Nehͻ."
  19,96,"Nokorε sε, wͻn a wͻagye adie na wͻdi dwumapa no Ahummͻborͻ Hene no de ͻdͻ bεma wͻn."
  19,97,"Enti Yayε (Qur’aan) no mmrε ama wo kεterεma, sεdeε wode bεhyԑ Nyame-surofoͻ no bᴐ, na wode bεbͻ wͻn a wͻreko tia dendeenden no nso kͻkͻ."
  19,98,"Awoͻ ntoatoasoͻ sεn na adi wͻn anim kan a Yasεe wͻn? Wohunu wͻn mu baako mpo, anaasε wote wͻ’nka anaasε wͻn ho mpopoeε bi?"
